fy: `go test ./pkg/store/... -v -run TestMakeValkeyOptions`\n449: \n450: - [ ] **T10.4** Test `makeValkeyOptions()` - Errors\n451:   - Test missing VALKEY_ADDR returns error\n452:   - Test missing password when required returns `ErrPasswordRequired`\n453:   - Verify: `go test ./pkg/store/... -v -run TestMakeValkeyOptions`\n454: \n455: - [ ] **T10.5** Test `initStore()` - Provider Selection\n456:   - Test STORE_TYPE=redis initializes redisStore\n457:   - Test STORE_TYPE=valkey initializes valkeyStore\n458:   - Test invalid/empty STORE_TYPE returns `ErrInvalidProvider`\n459:   - Test `Storage()` returns singleton\n460:   - Verify: `go test ./pkg/store/... -v -run TestInitStore`\n461: \n462: ### Phase 11: Integration Tests\n463: \n464: - [ ] **T11.1** Create `pkg/store/store_integration_test.go`\n465:   - Mark tests with `testing.Short()` skip\n466:   - Test against real Redis/Valkey if available\n467:   - Verify: `go test ./pkg/store/... -v -run Integration`\n468: \n469: - [ ] **T11.2** Test Redis integration - End-to-end\n470:   - Test create → get → update → delete flow\n471:   - Test ZSET indexing correctness\n472:   - Test expiry and activity queries\n473:   - Verify: `go test ./pkg/store/... -v -run IntegrationRedis`\n474: \n475: - [ ] **T11.3** Test Valkey integration - End-to-end\n476:   - Test full lifecycle operations\n477:   - Verify: `go test ./pkg/store/... -v -run IntegrationValkey`\n478: \n479: ### Phase 12: Validation & Quality\n480: \n481: - [ ] **T12.1** Run `go vet ./pkg/store/...`\n482:   - Fix any issues reported\n483:   - Verify: `go vet ./pkg/store/...`\n484: \n485: - [ ] **T12.2** Run `golangci-lint run ./pkg/store/...`\n486:   - Fix any linting issues\n487:   - Verify: `golangci-lint run ./pkg/store/...`\n488: \n489: - [ ] **T12.3** Run `go mod tidy`\n490:   - Clean up dependencies\n491:   - Verify: `go mod tidy && go mod verify`\n492: \n493: - [ ] **T12.4** Verify build\n494:   - Run: `go build ./pkg/store/...`\n495:   - Ensure no build errors