est ./pkg/store/... -v -run Integration` |\n554: | T12.1 | `go vet ./pkg/store/...` |\n555: | T12.2 | `golangci-lint run ./pkg/store/...` |\n556: | T12.3 | `go mod tidy && go mod verify` |\n557: | T12.4 | `go build ./pkg/store/...` |\n558: | T12.5 | `go test ./pkg/store/... -cover` |\n559: | T12.6 | `go test ./pkg/store/... -v -race` |\n560: \n561: ---\n562: \n563: ## Acceptance Criteria\n564: \n565: - [ ] Store interface 完整实现 (Redis + Valkey)\n566: - [ ] Singleton 模式正确实现\n567: - [ ] 支持环境变量配置\n568: - [ ] ZSET 索引正确维护 (expiry, last_activity)\n569: - [ ] Pipeline/DoMulti 原子操作正确\n570: - [ ] 错误处理完善 (ErrNotFound, validation errors)\n571: - [ ] Pass `go vet` with zero issues\n572: - [ ] Pass `golangci-lint` with zero issues\n573: - [ ] Unit tests pass with race detector\n574: - [ ] Test coverage ≥ 80%\n575: - [ ] 支持 miniredis 单元测试\n576: - [ ] Redis key 设计合理 (session:{id}, session:expiry, session:last_activity)\n577: - [ ] 支持 Ping 连接验证\n578: - [ ] 支持 ListExpiredSandboxes 和 ListInactiveSandboxes GC 查询\n579: - [ ] 支持 UpdateSessionLastActivity 活跃时间更新\n580: \n581: ---\n582: \n583: ## Notes\n584: \n585: - 使用 miniredis 进行 Redis 单元测试，避免依赖真实 Redis\n586: - Valkey 测试使用 mock，因 valkey-go 不提供轻量级测试工具\n587: - Pipeline/DoMulti 确保 StoreSandbox 和 DeleteSandboxBySessionID 的原子性\n588: - ZSET 索引设计支持高效的过期和活跃时间查询\n589: - 密码默认必需，可通过环境变量禁用用于本地开发\n590: - 后续可扩展: TLS 支持、集群 hash tags、连接池调优\n591: \n592: ---\n593: \n594: ## Implementation Timeline\n595: \n596: | Phase | Tasks | Status | Completion |\n597: |-------|-------|--------|------------|\n598: | Phase 1: Dependencies | T1.1-T1.4 | Not Started | 0% |\n599: | Phase 2: Interface & Types | T2.1-T2.5 | Not Started | 0% |\n600: | Phase 3: Redis Config | T3.1-T3.3 | Not Started | 0% |\n601: | Phase 4: Redis Methods | T4.1-T4.11 | Not Started | 0% |\n602: | Phase 5: Valkey Config | T5.1-T5.2 | Not Started | 0% |\n603: | Phase 6: Valkey Methods | T6.1-T6.10 | Not Started | 0% |\n604: | Phase 7: initStore | T7.1-T7.3 | Not Started | 0% |\n605: | Phase 8: Redis Tests | T8.1-T8.11 | Not Started | 0% |\n606: | Phase 9: Valkey Tests | T9.1-T9.10 | Not Started | 0% |\n607: | Phase 10: Config Tests | T10.1-T10.5 | Not Started | 0% |\n608: | Phase 11: Integration | T11.1-T11.3 | Not Started | 0% |\n609: | Phase 12: Validation | T12.1-T12.6 | Not Started | 0% |\n610: \n611: **Total Progress: 0% Complete**\n612: \n613: ---\n614: \n615: ## Key Design Decisions\n616: \n617: 1. **Two Providers**: Support both Redis (go-redis/v9) and Valkey (valkey-go) for flexibility\n618: 2. **ZSET Indexing**: Use sorted sets for expiry and activity queries (GC support)\n619: 3. **Atomic Operations**: Pipeline (Redis) and DoMulti (Valkey) for multi-key operations\n620: 4. **Singleton Pattern**: Single global store instance via `Storage()` function\n621: 5. **JSON Storage**: SandboxInfo stored as JSON documents in Redis keys\n622: 6. **Validation**: Reject invalid inputs (nil sandbox, zero expiresAt, empty sessionID)\n623: 7. **Environment Config**: All connection parameters via env vars for 12-factor app compliance\n\n(End of file - total 623 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-013 — Redis 存储实现 Tasks\n\n## Metadata\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-013 — Redis 存储实现 |\n| Module | `pkg/store` |\n| Language | Go |\n| Size | M |\n| Design | [Stage ST-3 completed] |\n\n---\n\n## Task Checklist\n\n### Phase 1: Dependencies Setup\n\n- [ ] **T1.1** Add Redis client dependency\n  - Run: `go get github.com/redis/go-redis/v9@latest`","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-013/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775858324811,"end":1775858324836}}}}
