{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775858389929,"sessionID":"ses_28698b365ffe7Q6RX8YJsvujiT","part":{"id":"prt_d79680aba001XRbj0VlqqDMNIQ","messageID":"msg_d7967c57e001sufXfXTi9RTFpi","sessionID":"ses_28698b365ffe7Q6RX8YJsvujiT","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_tool-187ff4f1d75244829f103d9baa1c0516","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-014/proposal.md","content":"# AR-014 — Valkey 存储实现 Proposal\n\n## Purpose\n\nImplement Valkey storage backend for AgentCube session management, providing high-performance, open-source Redis-compatible storage. This implementation provides:\n\n1. **Valkey Backend**: Pure Valkey implementation using `valkey-go` client library\n2. **Session Persistence**: Store `SandboxInfo` JSON documents keyed by session ID\n3. **GC Support**: Sorted sets for expiry-based and last-activity-based queries\n4. **Configuration**: Environment-based connection configuration\n\n## Scope\n\n### In Scope\n\n| Deliverable | Description |\n|-------------|-------------|\n| `pkg/store/valkey.go` | ValkeyStore struct implementing Store interface |\n| `pkg/store/valkey_config.go` | Valkey configuration management |\n| `pkg/store/valkey_test.go` | Unit tests for Valkey implementation |\n\n### Key Components\n\n```\npkg/store/\n├── ValkeyStore struct (valkey.go)\n│   ├── cli valkey.Client\n│   ├── sessionPrefix = \"session:\"\n│   ├── expiryIndexKey = \"session:expiry\"\n│   └── lastActivityIndexKey = \"session:last_activity\"\n│\n├── Configuration (valkey_config.go)\n│   ├── VALKEY_ADDR (comma-separated addresses)\n│   ├── VALKEY_PASSWORD\n│   ├── VALKEY_PASSWORD_REQUIRED\n│   ├── VALKEY_DISABLE_CACHE\n│   └── VALKEY_FORCE_SINGLE\n│\n└── Test Coverage (valkey_test.go)\n    ├── Ping connectivity\n    ├── CRUD operations\n    ├── ZSET index operations\n    ├── ErrNotFound scenarios\n```\n\n### Out of Scope\n\n- Redis implementation (covered in AR-013)\n- Valkey Cluster deployment (single-node focus)\n- Distributed lock implementation\n- Data migration tools\n- TLS connection support\n\n## Impact Analysis\n\n### Upstream Dependencies\n\n| Dependency | Impact |\n|------------|--------|\n| `github.com/valkey-io/valkey-go` | Valkey client library |\n| `k8s.io/klog/v2` | Logging |\n| `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/common/types` | SandboxInfo struct |\n| AR-012 | Store interface definition |\n\n### Downstream Consumers\n\n| Consumer | Usage |\n|----------|-------|\n| Session Manager | Query/create/update sessions |\n| Router | Session lookup for routing |\n| Garbage Collector | ListExpiredSandboxes / ListInactiveSandboxes |\n\n## Risks\n\n| Risk | Mitigation |\n|------|------------|\n| Valkey connection failure | Env validation on init; Ping for health check |\n| Missing password with required=true | Explicit env check |\n| Key collision | Use globally unique session ID |\n\n## References\n\n- AR-012 — Store interface definition\n- AR-013 — Redis implementation (reference)\n- [valkey-go](https://github.com/valkey-io/valkey-go)"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-014/proposal.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-014/proposal.md","time":{"start":1775858389910,"end":1775858389928}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775858389931,"sessionID":"ses_28698b365ffe7Q6RX8YJsvujiT","part":{"id":"prt_d79682611001jaIon2mzZxgcAR","messageID":"msg_d7967c57e001sufXfXTi9RTFpi","sessionID":"ses_28698b365ffe7Q6RX8YJsvujiT","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_tool-2dcd1b77ab784ae5b98d52ac882d32c8","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-014/spec.md","content":"# AR-014 — Valkey 存储实现\n\n## Metadata\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-014 — Valkey 存储实现 |\n| Module | `pkg/store` |\n| Language | Go |\n| Size | S |\n| Stage | ST-0 |\n\n## Scope\n\n实现 Valkey 存储后端，包括:\n- `ValkeyStore` 结构实现 Store 接口\n- Valkey 配置管理\n- Session 序列化/反序列化\n- 错误处理\n\n## Out of Scope\n\n- Redis 实现 (AR-013)\n- Valkey 集群支持\n- 分布式锁\n- TLS 连接\n\n## Dependencies\n\n| Dependency | Version | Purpose |\n|------------|---------|---------|\n| AR-012 | - | Store 接口定义 |\n| valkey-go | latest | Valkey 客户端 |\n\n## Deliverables\n\n| File | Description |\n|------|-------------|\n| `pkg/store/valkey.go` | ValkeyStore 实现 |\n| `pkg/store/valkey_config.go` | Valkey 配置结构 |\n| `pkg/store/valkey_test.go` | 单元测试 |\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n\n- [ ] 实现完整的 Store 接口\n- [ ] 支持配置化连接参数\n- [ ] 处理所有错误情况\n- [ ] 通过 `go vet` 和 `golangci-lint`\n- [ ] 单元测试覆盖率 ≥ 80%\n\n## References\n\n- AR-012 — Store 接口定义\n- AR-013 — Redis 实现"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-014/spec.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-014/spec.md","time":{"start":1775858389914,"end":1775858389930}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775858389933,"sessionID":"ses_28698b365ffe7Q6RX8YJsvujiT","part":{"id":"prt_d79685701001frje1qgLy9kBuZ","messageID":"msg_d7967c57e001sufXfXTi9RTFpi","sessionID":"ses_28698b365ffe7Q6RX8YJsvujiT","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_tool-c6bc93198d6f47209ad5a2f3b74f4c0a","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-014/design.md","content":"# AR-014 — Valkey 存储实现 Design\n\n## Overview\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-014 — Valkey 存储实现 |\n| Module | `pkg/store` |\n| Language | Go |\n| Size | S |\n| Stage | ST-1 |\n\n实现 Valkey 存储后端，提供高性能的会话持久化能力，支持按过期时间和最后活跃时间索引以便垃圾回收。\n\n## Architecture\n\n```\n┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│                      Application Layer                       │\n│                    (Session Manager, GC)                      │\n└────────────────────────────────┬─────────────────────────────┘\n                                  │\n                                  v\n┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│                    Store Interface                            │\n│  Ping / Get / Store / Update / Delete / List* / Close        │\n└────────────────────────────────┬─────────────────────────────┘\n                                  │\n                                  v\n┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│                    ValkeyStore                                │\n│                  (valkey-go Client)                           │\n└────────────────────────────────┬─────────────────────────────┘\n                                  │\n                                  v\n┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│                    Valkey Server                              │\n│                  (Single/Cluster)                             │\n└──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n```\n\n## Data Structures\n\n### ValkeyStore Struct\n\n```go\ntype ValkeyStore struct {\n    cli                  valkey.Client\n    sessionPrefix        string\n    expiryIndexKey       string\n    lastActivityIndexKey string\n}\n```\n\n### Key Design\n\n| Key Pattern | Type | Purpose |\n|-------------|------|---------|\n| `session:{id}` | String | JSON document storing SandboxInfo |\n| `session:expiry` | ZSET | Index by expiry timestamp |\n| `session:last_activity` | ZSET | Index by last activity |\n\n## Configuration\n\n| Variable | Required | Default | Description |\n|----------|----------|---------|-------------|\n| `VALKEY_ADDR` | Yes | - | Comma-separated addresses |\n| `VALKEY_PASSWORD` | Conditional | - | Password |\n| `VALKEY_PASSWORD_REQUIRED` | No | `true` | Disable password requirement |\n| `VALKEY_DISABLE_CACHE` | No | `false` | Disable client-side cache |\n| `VALKEY_FORCE_SINGLE` | No | `false` | Force single client mode |\n\n## File Structure\n\n```\npkg/store/\n  valkey.go           — ValkeyStore implementation\n  valkey_config.go    — Configuration helper\n  valkey_test.go      — Unit tests\n```\n\n## Dependencies\n\n| Package | Version | Purpose |\n|---------|---------|---------|\n| `github.com/valkey-io/valkey-go` | latest | Valkey client |\n| `k8s.io/klog/v2` | latest | Logging |\n\n## References\n\n- AR-012 — Store interface\n- AR-013 — Redis implementation\n- valkey-go: https://github.com/valkey-io/valkey-go"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-014/design.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-014/design.md","time":{"start":1775858389917,"end":1775858389932}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775858389936,"sessionID":"ses_28698b365ffe7Q6RX8YJsvujiT","part":{"id":"prt_d79689372001L7InvU4pGPEXGl","messageID":"msg_d7967c57e001sufXfXTi9RTFpi","sessionID":"ses_28698b365ffe7Q6RX8YJsvujiT","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_tool-69be11b33dff40559a0b83169bca4b4c","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-014/tasks.md","content":"# AR-014 — Valkey 存储实现 Tasks\n\n## Metadata\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-014 — Valkey 存储实现 |\n| Module | `pkg/store` |\n| Language | Go |\n| Size | S |\n| Design | [Stage ST-1 pending] |\n\n---\n\n## Task Checklist\n\n### Phase 1: Dependencies Setup\n\n- [ ] **T1.1** Add Valkey client dependency\n  - Run: `go get github.com/valkey-io/valkey-go@latest`\n  - Verify: `go mod tidy && go mod verify`\n\n- [ ] **T1.2** Verify Store interface exists\n  - Check: AR-012 provides Store interface\n  - Verify required methods: Ping, Get, Store, Update, Delete, List*, Close\n\n### Phase 2: Valkey Implementation\n\n- [ ] **T2.1** Create `pkg/store/valkey.go` - Struct Definition\n  - Define `ValkeyStore struct`\n  - Implement `NewValkeyStore()` constructor\n  - Verify: `go build ./pkg/store/`\n\n- [ ] **T2.2** Create `pkg/store/valkey_config.go` - Configuration\n  - Implement `makeValkeyOptions()`\n  - Read env vars: VALKEY_ADDR, VALKEY_PASSWORD, etc.\n  - Verify: `go build ./pkg/store/`\n\n- [ ] **T2.3** Implement Store interface methods\n  - Ping(ctx)\n  - GetSandboxBySessionID(ctx, sessionID)\n  - StoreSandbox(ctx, sandbox)\n  - UpdateSandbox(ctx, sandbox)\n  - DeleteSandboxBySessionID(ctx, sessionID)\n  - ListExpiredSandboxes(ctx, before, limit)\n  - ListInactiveSandboxes(ctx, before, limit)\n  - UpdateSessionLastActivity(ctx, sessionID, at)\n  - Close()\n  - Verify: `go build ./pkg/store/`\n\n### Phase 3: Unit Tests\n\n- [ ] **T3.1** Create `pkg/store/valkey_test.go` - Test Setup\n  - Create test helpers\n  - Create mock valkey.Client\n  - Verify: `go test ./pkg/store/... -v`\n\n- [ ] **T3.2** Test CRUD operations\n  - Test Get/Store/Update/Delete\n  - Test ErrNotFound handling\n  - Verify: `go test ./pkg/store/... -v`\n\n- [ ] **T3.3** Test ZSET index operations\n  - Test ListExpiredSandboxes\n  - Test ListInactiveSandboxes\n  - Verify: `go test ./pkg/store/... -v`\n\n### Phase 4: Validation\n\n- [ ] **T4.1** Run `go vet ./pkg/store/...`\n- [ ] **T4.2** Run `golangci-lint run ./pkg/store/...`\n- [ ] **T4.3** Verify test coverage ≥ 80%\n- [ ] **T4.4** Run tests with race detector\n\n---\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n\n- [ ] ValkeyStore 完整实现 Store 接口\n- [ ] 支持环境变量配置\n- [ ] ZSET 索引正确维护\n- [ ] 错误处理完善\n- [ ] Pass `go vet`\n- [ ] Pass `golangci-lint`\n- [ ] Test coverage ≥ 80%\n\n---\n\n## Notes\n\n- 参考 AR-013 Redis 实现的 API 设计\n- 使用 valkey-go 的 B() builder 模式构建命令\n- DoMulti 用于原子操作"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-014/tasks.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-014/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775858389920,"end":1775858389934}}}}
